Definition: an expression of some desire or inclination
Example: I could tell that it was his wish that the guests leave; his crying was an indirect request for attention
Synonyms: verb, emotion, communication, indirect_request, request, an, expression, of, some, desire, or, inclination, I, could, tell, that, it, was, his, the, guests, leave, crying, indirect, for, attention
Category: noun.communication
